<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN" [
<!ENTITY date "$FreeBSD: www/register.sgml,v 1.2 2003/12/10 18:20:18 ebrandi Exp $">
<!ENTITY title "Register">
<!ENTITY % includes SYSTEM "includes.sgml"> %includes;
]>

<html>
    &header;

    <center><font size="4">Inscreva-se nas listas de discuss&atilde;o 
    announce@FreeBSD.org e security-announce@FreeBSD.org.</font></center>

    <p>A lista de discuss&atilde;o announce@FreeBSD.org &eacute; utilizada para
    comunicar importantes eventos do projeto, como por exemplo novos
    releases, eventos marcantes e avisos de seguran&ccedil;a.</p>
    
    <p>
    Os avisos de seguran&ccedil;a s&atilde;o sempre comunicados atrav&eacute;s da lista de
    discuss&atilde;o security-notifications@FreeBSD.org (observe que a
    announce@FreeBSD.org j&aacute; engloba esta lista, de forma que n&atilde;o &eacute;
    necess&aacute;rio se inscrever em ambas).</p>
    
    <form action="http://www.FreeBSD.org/cgi/reg.cgi" method="post">
      <input type="hidden" name="recipient" value="majordomo@FreeBSD.org"><br>
      <input type="hidden" name="version" value="Web-Registration">

      <center>
	  <table width="75%" border="0">
	  <tr>
	    <td>Endere&ccedil;o de Email: </td>
	    
	    <td align="left"><input type="text" name="emaila"
		size="30"></td>
	  </tr>
	  
	  <tr>
	    <td>Op&ccedil;&atilde;o para a lista announce@FreeBSD.org: </td>

	    <td><input type="radio" name="announce" value="yes">
	    Inscrever-se<br>
	      <input type="radio" name="announce" value="no">
	      Desinscrever-se</td>
	  </tr>

	  <tr>
	    <td>Op&ccedil;&atilde;o para a lista security-notifications@FreeBSD.org: </td>

	    <td><input type="radio" name="security-notifications" value="yes"> Inscrever-se<br>
	      <input type="radio" name="security-notifications" value="no"> Desinscrever-se</td>
	  </tr>
	</table>

	<p><input type="submit" value="Enviar">
	  <input type="reset" value="Limpar"></p>
      </center>
    </form>
    
      &footer;
  </body>
</html>

